      • RunnableBatch

        public RunnableBatch(MaskingAlgorithm<T> algorithmIn,
                     int batchSize)
        Create a runnable batch associated with a particular algorithm. This method will perform slightly better when the batch size is known in advance. The batch may grow larger than the initial size.
        Parameters:
        algorithmIn - The algorithm to use when running the batch.
        batchSize - The initial size of the batch.
